        <li>REAL NAME OF RAJESH KHANNA IS: <b>JATIN KHANNA</b></li><br>
        <li>Born: 29th December, 1942. </li><br>
        <li>First debut: 1966 in the movie "Aakhri Khat"</li><br>
        <li>In 2005, he was honored with Filmfare Lifetime Achievement Award</li><br>
        <li>He became the memeber of the Parliament between 1992 and 1996</li><br>
        <li>He married Dimple Kapadia in March, 1973</li><br>
        <li>Died: 18th July, 2012 at the age of 69</li><br>
